news.title: Gurugram: MCG commissioner orders officials to ensure construction sites follow GRAP norms
news.para: According to the corporation, it is mandatory for all construction sites to have smog guns and other equipment for dust mitigation.

news.title: Consumer forum directs Puma Realtors to execute sale deed of flat or face action
news.para: Complainant Nirmal Milkha Singh had filed a consumer complaint in 2016 before the commission, seeking possession of the flat purchased by her in the housing project in Mohali.

news.title: Buildings near Supertech twin towers demolition site safe: CBRI
news.para: The institute has been studying the post-demolition structural audit report (PDSAR), prepared and sent by the SEC in the first week of October.

news.title: Gurugram civic body issues notices to developers of 15 buildings
news.para: At the same time, a probe has been ordered to fix the responsibility of officials who were involved in the issuance of the NOCs to these buildings in clear violation of norms, TOI has learnt.

news.title: Ghaziabad: NCDRC orders builder to refund buyers for flat delivery delay
news.para: In June this year, UP-RERA cancelled the registrations of the three projects -- Antriksh Sanskriti Phase-2, Antriksh Sanskriti Phase-3 and Raksha Vigyaan Sanskriti Phase-2 -- located adjacent to NH-9 in Pratap Vihar, for the delay in delivery.

news.title: CJI-led bench to hold special sitting on Oct 22 to hear Amrapali case
news.para: The CJI said his tenure is coming to an end and he would not have much time to adjudicate all the pending issues of the Amrapali Group.

news.title: UltraTech Cement's net profit falls 42% to Rs 759 crore in Q2 FY23
news.para: Its revenue from operations rose 15.61 per cent to Rs 13,892.69 crore during the quarter under review as against Rs 12,016.78 crore in the corresponding period of the last fiscal.

news.title: Karza Technologies co-founder buys duplex in Mumbai for Rs 47.70 crore
news.para: Shirhatti has bought the apartment in Samarpan Building, Off Carter Road, directly from the developer Raghuleela Estates, a subsidiary of the Wadhwa Group.

news.title: Mukesh Ambani splurges $163 million on priciest Dubai villa
news.para: Mukesh Ambani bought the Palm Jumeirah mansion last week for about $163 million from the family of Kuwaiti tycoon Mohammed Alshaya, said the people, asking not to be named as they’re not authorized to speak publicly.

news.title: Prestige Estates' sales bookings rise 66% to Rs 3,511 crore in Q2 FY23
news.para: During the April-September period of this fiscal, Prestige Group's sales bookings more than doubled to Rs 6,523.1 crore from Rs 2,845.9 crore in the corresponding period of the previous year.

news.title: Hong Kong cuts property tax, eases visa rules to attract talent
news.para: The property rule will refund extra stamp duties that non-permanent resident property buyers have to pay after they have stayed in the city for seven years.

news.title: Dehradun: Notices to 82 government departments for property tax default
news.para: DMC is in the process of identifying tax defaulters and had sent notices to individuals as well earlier this month. Few government departments had also been notified a couple of months ago.

news.title: Hyderabad: Land document scam busted, five realty agents land in police dragnet
news.para: Police seized four forged sale deed documents, fake government stamps, non-judicial stamp papers, a car and eight cell phones from their possession.

news.title: Vadodara: Seven new proposed town planning schemes to be taken up
news.para: The seven schemes include two each Kalali and Harni-Darjipura and one each in Jambuva, Maneja and Vadsar. The agenda for the meeting seeks to authorize the municipal commissioner to conduct further processes for these schemes.

news.title: Andhra Pradesh: Ensure flawless land resurvey, officials told
news.para: The survey, conducted with the involvement of thousands of recruited people and by spending crores of rupees for purchase of modern survey equipment, should give no room for others to point fingers.
